narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Definitely recommend, but if you're reading this, you're probably on the screenwriting track already...
This is the class to take if you want to spend a full year writing a screen play. It's a challenge but totally worth it. DO IT.

Take this only if you're ready to take on a 90 page plus writing project!! You need to be seriously committed to the class AND your story. I'd definitely recommend it for film studies majors seeking a more creative option for their thesis.
